│ for ULT with RHS all-ones, we should avoid returning false unless LHS_CR.isFullSet() or LHS_CR.getLower() >=    │
│ RHS. I will modify simplifyICmpWithConstant to special-case ULT with all-ones and prevent incorrect folding.    │
